"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"merge_method":"squash","commit_title":"plbonuslib: match fn_8003F294 (#2565)","commit_message":"* match: fn_8003F294 (stale-move-table maintenance) — 100%\n\nDecompiles fn_8003F294 in src/melee/pl/plbonuslib.c, the per-frame\nstale-move-table maintenance helper called by pl_8003FAA8 alongside\nfn_8003EE2C and fn_8003F53C. 680-byte body, instruction-identical match.\n\nKey levers:\n- Two threshold locals (unsigned int threshold, int threshold2) carrying the\n  pl_804D6470 entries into pl_8003906C calls, with inline assignments at the\n  call sites to control register flow.\n- Helper inline plBonusLib_8003F294_inline(stats, attack) wrapping the\n  pl_800386D8 lookup, used for kinds 0x6B / 0x70 / 0x6F.\n- Local int e8 hoisting the pl_800386E8 result for the kind 0x49 call.\n- f32 x8c reinterpret of pl_804D6470->x8C feeding pl_80039238 alongside the\n  sqrtf__Ff magnitude of (xCDC,xCE0).\n- u32 xb8 / u32 v locals in the trailing pl_8003906C(-1, ...) branch to keep\n  the comparison and write to xD5C in expected order.\n- PAD_STACK(24) preserved.\n- (unsigned int) cast on pl_804D6470->xE4 because the field is currently\n  typed UNK_T (void*) in src/melee/pl/types.h; the cast is purely to satisfy\n  -requireprotos and does not affect codegen.\n\nVerified via tools/checkdiff.py: match=true match_percent=100.00\nclassification=instruction-identical. Surrounding fn_8003EE2C, fn_8003F53C,\npl_8003FAA8 and plBonusLib_8003D514 unchanged at 100%.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* style: clang-format fn_8003F294 body in plbonuslib.c\n\nWhitespace-only reformat applied by the pre-commit clang-format pass on the\nprevious commit. fn_8003F294 still matches at match=true match_percent=100.00\n(verified via tools/checkdiff.py after rebuild).\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: itsgrimetime <990274+itsgrimetime@users.noreply.github.com>\nCo-authored-by: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>"},"assignee":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"merged":true,"mergeable":null,"rebaseable":null,"mergeable_state":"unknown","merged_by":{"login":"ribbanya","id":5190964,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjUxOTA5NjQ=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/5190964?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya","html_url":"https://github.com/ribbanya","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"comments":1,"review_comments":0,"maintainer_can_modify":false,"commits":3,"additions":74,"deletions":1,"changed_files":1}